@Monk
$
$Well, here it is. The last board I've
$made in this confusing adventure. I
$probably won't finish it, because
$frankly, getting this far was goddamned
$draining, and there's four more dungeons,
$as well as five more bosses. I'm afraid
$I'm just a lazy gent, and there's the
$matter of Crankgod RPG, which Crank
$expects me to actually work on. So here
$it is, guys. That's all she wrote.
$
/i
